{
  "stem": "7860.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I remember many drunks would show up in our neighborhood, beat us if there was anybody in sight.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody resisted them for fear if they would resist them, there would be a pogrom, known as a pogrom in the United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's why they left me alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was-- so before the end-- before the war started, I remember there was an organization, Betar-- they're under [NON-ENGLISH], they fought back in organized fashion.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They fought back any hooligans like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although my father coming home with a big canister of soda from the circumcision of my youngest brother Ruven, the Poles, hooligans, whole bunch of men, beat him up, left him for dead because he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although he was not bearded-- he was clean shaven, bare-headed-- not indicating he's a Jew, but they recognized him as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they left him for dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They beat him on the way home from--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the way home-- no, come home carrying a big canister of soda, seltzer water, so-- for the circumcision, preparing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to me, I didn't see no changes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Things just happen to be-- information more or less to me as a child's eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that about three planes were flying overhead, and they were bombing primarily the Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I mentioned, but I couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Voiced my protest to my mother-- why don't anybody do something about it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then nobody did anything for us later on either.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I do remember there were lines for water, lines to the bakery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Jews were pulled out of those lines and beaten up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No-- couldn't go by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the war just started but the Germans didn't even come in yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
